---
layout: false
metaTitle: "The Voice Capture Template | EcomGhosts"
metaDescription: "The exact process I use before writing a single LinkedIn post for ecommerce founders. 15 questions to extract your authentic voice. Free template from EcomGhosts."
permalink: /voice-capture/
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block head %}
<style>
    /* Landing Page Specific Styles */
    .lp-hero {
        padding: 10rem 0 4rem;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, var(--dark-bg-alt) 100%);
    }

    .lp-hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .lp-hero-content {
        max-width: 620px;
    }

    .lp-eyebrow {
        color: var(--orange-primary);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lp-headline {
        font-size: 2.75rem;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--white);
    }

    .lp-subheadline {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--light-gray);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .lp-proof {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }

    .lp-proof-avatar {
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 2px solid var(--orange-primary);
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .lp-proof-text {
        color: var(--text-gray);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .lp-proof-text strong {
        color: var(--light-gray);
    }

    /* Signup Card */
    .lp-signup-card {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg-card);
        border: 2px solid var(--border-light);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .lp-signup-card:hover {
        border-color: var(--orange-primary);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.15);
    }

    .lp-card-badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: -12px;
        left: 24px;
        background-color: var(--orange-primary);
        color: var(--white);
        padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .lp-card-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--white);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lp-card-desc {
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .lp-includes {
        list-style: none;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .lp-includes li {
        padding: 0.6rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.75rem;
        position: relative;
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .lp-includes li:before {
        content: "\2713";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--orange-primary);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Substack Embed Styling */
    .lp-form-container {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .lp-form-container iframe {
        border: none !important;
        background: transparent !important;
    }

    .lp-no-spam {
        color: var(--text-gray);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Problem Section */
    .lp-problem {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .lp-problem-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .lp-problem-card {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg-card);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .lp-problem-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lp-problem-card h3 {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .lp-problem-card p {
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* What's Inside Section */
    .lp-inside {
        background-color: var(--dark-charcoal);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .lp-inside-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .lp-inside-list {
        list-style: none;
    }

    .lp-inside-list li {
        padding: 1.25rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .lp-inside-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .lp-inside-number {
        color: var(--orange-primary);
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        min-width: 2rem;
    }

    .lp-inside-text h4 {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .lp-inside-text p {
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .lp-inside-preview {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg-card);
        border: 2px solid var(--border-light);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .lp-preview-label {
        color: var(--orange-primary);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .lp-preview-question {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .lp-preview-hint {
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .lp-preview-example {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        border-left: 3px solid var(--orange-primary);
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .lp-preview-example p {
        color: var(--text-gray);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .lp-preview-divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    /* Who It's For Section */
    .lp-who {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg-alt);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .lp-who-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .lp-who-card {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg-card);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }

    .lp-who-card h3 {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .lp-who-card ul {
        list-style: none;
    }

    .lp-who-card ul li {
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .lp-who-yes li:before {
        content: "\2713";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #22C55E;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .lp-who-no li:before {
        content: "\2717";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #EF4444;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Bottom CTA Section */
    .lp-bottom-cta {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange-primary) 0%, var(--orange-hover) 100%);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .lp-bottom-cta-content {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .lp-bottom-cta h2 {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lp-bottom-cta p {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .lp-bottom-form {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .lp-bottom-form iframe {
        border: none !important;
        background: transparent !important;
    }

    /* Author Section */
    .lp-author {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .lp-author-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .lp-author-photo {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 3px solid var(--orange-primary);
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .lp-author-name {
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .lp-author-title-text {
        color: var(--orange-primary);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .lp-author-bio {
        color: var(--light-gray);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .lp-hero-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        .lp-hero-content {
            max-width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .lp-proof {
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .lp-signup-card {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .lp-inside-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .lp-hero {
            padding: 8rem 0 3rem;
        }

        .lp-headline {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .lp-problem-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .lp-who-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .lp-author-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .lp-author-photo {
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    }
</style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="lp-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="lp-hero-grid">
                <div class="lp-hero-content">
                    <p class="lp-eyebrow">Free Template</p>
                    <h1 class="lp-headline">The exact process I use before writing a single LinkedIn post for ecommerce founders</h1>
                    <p class="lp-subheadline">
                        Most ghostwriting fails because the writer never captured the founder's voice. This is the 15-question template I use with every EcomGhosts client. It takes 30 minutes. It changes everything.
                    </p>
                    <div class="lp-proof">
                        <img src="/img/john-aspinall.jpg" alt="John Aspinall" class="lp-proof-avatar">
                        <p class="lp-proof-text">
                            <strong>John Aspinall</strong> grew from 3K to 25K LinkedIn followers using this exact voice-first approach.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lp-signup-card">
                    <div class="lp-card-badge">Free Download</div>
                    <h2 class="lp-card-title">Get the Voice Capture Template</h2>
                    <p class="lp-card-desc">15 questions. 30 minutes. A documented voice that makes every post sound like you.</p>
                    <ul class="lp-includes">
                        <li>15 voice extraction questions with examples</li>
                        <li>Voice profile summary framework</li>
                        <li>Instructions for solo use or with a ghostwriter</li>
                        <li>The same template used by 10+ ecom founders</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="lp-form-container">
                        <iframe src="https://johnaspinallsr.substack.com/embed" width="100%" height="150" style="background: transparent;" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>
                    </div>
                    <p class="lp-no-spam">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. You'll also get operator-level LinkedIn insights.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="lp-problem">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-headline center">Why most ghostwritten content sounds fake</h2>
            <div class="lp-problem-grid">
                <div class="lp-problem-card">
                    <div class="lp-problem-icon">&#9888;</div>
                    <h3>They skip voice capture</h3>
                    <p>Most ghostwriters jump straight to writing. No voice interview. No style profiling. No wonder it sounds like a marketing agency wrote it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="lp-problem-card">
                    <div class="lp-problem-icon">&#9888;</div>
                    <h3>They don't speak ecom</h3>
                    <p>A generalist writer doesn't know ACOS from BSR. Your audience can tell when the person behind the post has never managed a listing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="lp-problem-card">
                    <div class="lp-problem-icon">&#9888;</div>
                    <h3>They write for engagement, not pipeline</h3>
                    <p>Viral hooks and motivational fluff might get likes. They don't get you on the shortlist for partnerships, speaking gigs, or inbound deals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What's Inside Section -->
    <section class="lp-inside">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-headline center white">What's inside the template</h2>
            <div class="lp-inside-grid">
                <ul class="lp-inside-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="lp-inside-number">01</span>
                        <div class="lp-inside-text">
                            <h4>Expertise Identity</h4>
                            <p>Define what you should be known for, your credibility number, and the industry frustration that fuels your best content.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="lp-inside-number">02</span>
                        <div class="lp-inside-text">
                            <h4>Communication Style</h4>
                            <p>Map your natural explanation patterns, verbal fingerprints, and tone so content matches how you actually talk.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="lp-inside-number">03</span>
                        <div class="lp-inside-text">
                            <h4>Your Stories</h4>
                            <p>Extract your origin story, key failure, and go-to client example. The raw material for content that connects.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="lp-inside-number">04</span>
                        <div class="lp-inside-text">
                            <h4>Your Opinions</h4>
                            <p>Document your contrarian beliefs, professional hills to die on, and mission. This is where your best content lives.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="lp-inside-number">05</span>
                        <div class="lp-inside-text">
                            <h4>Voice Profile Summary</h4>
                            <p>Compile everything into a one-page voice profile you can tape to your wall or hand to any writer.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="lp-inside-preview">
                    <p class="lp-preview-label">Sample Question</p>
                    <p class="lp-preview-question">What have you done more of than almost anyone you know?</p>
                    <p class="lp-preview-hint">Think in numbers. Accounts managed. Products launched. Revenue generated. Campaigns run.</p>
                    <div class="lp-preview-example">
                        <p>"I've reviewed 50,000 listings" hits different than "I'm experienced in Amazon."</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="lp-preview-divider">
                    <p class="lp-preview-question">What does your industry get wrong that makes you want to flip a table?</p>
                    <p class="lp-preview-hint">Be specific. Not "people don't invest in creative."</p>
                    <div class="lp-preview-example">
                        <p>"Sellers spend $30K/month on PPC driving traffic to a hero image they spent $50 on."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Who It's For Section -->
    <section class="lp-who">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-headline center">Is this for you?</h2>
            <div class="lp-who-grid">
                <div class="lp-who-card">
                    <h3>This template is for you if:</h3>
                    <ul class="lp-who-yes">
                        <li>You're an ecommerce founder or Amazon operator with deep expertise</li>
                        <li>You know you should be posting on LinkedIn but can't sustain it</li>
                        <li>You've hired a ghostwriter before and the content sounded generic</li>
                        <li>You want to build authority that drives real business outcomes</li>
                        <li>You're evaluating whether to write your own content or hire help</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="lp-who-card">
                    <h3>This is NOT for you if:</h3>
                    <ul class="lp-who-no">
                        <li>You're looking for viral hooks and engagement hacks</li>
                        <li>You want motivational or inspirational content templates</li>
                        <li>You're not in ecommerce (this is built for operators)</li>
                        <li>You think LinkedIn is just for job seekers</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Author Section -->
    <section class="lp-author">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="lp-author-grid">
                <img src="/img/john-aspinall.jpg" alt="John Aspinall" class="lp-author-photo">
                <div>
                    <p class="lp-author-name">John Aspinall</p>
                    <p class="lp-author-title-text">Founder, EcomGhosts</p>
                    <p class="lp-author-bio">
                        20 years in ecommerce. 14,000+ hero images optimized. 50,000+ listings reviewed. Grew from 3,000 to 25,000 LinkedIn followers by narrowing to one niche and posting content that sounds like an operator, not a marketer. Founded EcomGhosts to give ecommerce founders the same system. This template is step one of every client engagement.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA Section -->
    <section class="lp-bottom-cta">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="lp-bottom-cta-content">
                <h2>Get the Voice Capture Template</h2>
                <p>15 questions. 30 minutes. The foundation for LinkedIn content that actually sounds like you.</p>
                <div class="lp-bottom-form">
                    <iframe src="https://johnaspinallsr.substack.com/embed" width="100%" height="150" style="background: transparent;" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
